<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 - Page Not Found</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ece9e6, #ffffff);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .container-404 {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px;
            max-width: 600px;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .container-404 h1 {
            font-size: 100px;
            margin: 0;
            color: #ff6b6b;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .container-404 h2 {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #333;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        .container-404 p {
            color: #666;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .btn-home {
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: red;
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            font-size: 18px;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .btn-home:hover {
            color: #ffffff;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container-404">
        <h1>404</h1>
        <h2>Oops! Page Not Found</h2>
        <p>The page you are looking for might have been removed, or is temporarily unavailable.</p>
        <a href="/" class="btn btn-home">Take Me Home</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
